Hello! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. My name is Jamie. May I ask who I'm speaking with today?

Hi Jamie, this is Alex.

Hi Alex, nice to speak with you! How can I assist you with your billing inquiry today?

I'm having some issues with the last invoice I received and would like to understand the charges.

Certainly! I can help with that. Could I have your billing account number to pull up your invoice details? Please read it out by digits.

Sure, it's two zero five eight three one seven.

Thank you, Alex. Just a moment while I access your account. Can you also confirm the last four digits of your phone number for verification?

Yes, the last four digits are one two three four.

Great, thank you for that. I see that your last invoice includes charges for the event package you booked. Do you have any specific questions about these charges?

I just wanted to confirm the total amount, it seemed higher than expected.

I understand. The total amount from the last invoice was two hundred fifty dollars. It includes the event space and catering services. If there’s anything specific, I can explain further. Otherwise, everything seems in order.

Thank you for clarifying, Jamie. That makes sense now.

You're welcome, Alex! If there's nothing else, I'd like to thank you for your time today. Feel free to call us if you have any more questions in the future. Have a great day!
